create_time.description: The timestamp when the resource was created. See https://google.aip.dev/148#timestamps.

effective_labels.description: All of labels (key/value pairs) present on the resource in GCP, including the labels configured through Terraform, other clients and services.

intercept_endpoint_group.description: The endpoint group that this association is connected to, for example: 'projects/123456789/locations/global/interceptEndpointGroups/my-eg'. See https://google.aip.dev/124.

intercept_endpoint_group_association_id.description: The ID to use for the new association, which will become the final component of the endpoint group's resource name. If not provided, the server will generate a unique ID.

labels.description: Labels are key/value pairs that help to organize and filter resources. **Note**: This field is non-authoritative, and will only manage the labels present in your configuration. Please refer to the field 'effective_labels' for all of the labels present on the resource.

location.description: The cloud location of the association, currently restricted to 'global'.

locations.description: The list of locations where the association is configured. This information is retrieved from the linked endpoint group.

locations_details.description: The list of locations where the association is present. This information is retrieved from the linked endpoint group, and not configured as part of the association itself.

name.description: The resource name of this endpoint group association, for example: 'projects/123456789/locations/global/interceptEndpointGroupAssociations/my-eg-association'. See https://google.aip.dev/122 for more details.

network.description: The VPC network that is associated. for example: 'projects/123456789/global/networks/my-network'. See https://google.aip.dev/124.

reconciling.description: The current state of the resource does not match the user's intended state, and the system is working to reconcile them. This part of the normal operation (e.g. adding a new location to the target deployment group). See https://google.aip.dev/128.

state.description: Current state of the endpoint group association. Possible values: STATE_UNSPECIFIED ACTIVE CREATING DELETING CLOSED OUT_OF_SYNC DELETE_FAILED

terraform_labels.description: The combination of labels configured directly on the resource and default labels configured on the provider.

update_time.description: The timestamp when the resource was most recently updated. See https://google.aip.dev/148#timestamps.
